        I was responsible for backend API development, Firebase Authentication implementation,
        iOS app implementation with SwiftUI, and CI/CD construction using Xcode Cloud and GitHub.
        In particular, I implemented the entire iOS app migration from UIKit to SwiftUI from scratch by myself.
      </div>
